Syntax: riposte

Prepares a riposte -- a counter-attack triggered when you successfully
parry an opponent's strike. Riposte is a Warrior-line finisher skill:
it can only be activated when your combo counter has reached the required
threshold during active combat.

Effects when activated:
  - Grants a +1 hitroll bonus for (combo_count - 3) combat rounds.
  - The combo counter is reset after activation.
  - Skill proficiency improves on successful use.

The hitroll bonus improves the accuracy of all subsequent attacks during
its duration. Pair riposte with the parry passive skill for best results.

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat.
  - Requires a valid finisher combo count (combo threshold met).
  - Must have the skill learned.

See also: shelp riposte parry fleche anti magic shell shieldblock
